{"data":[{"date":"10:21 17/08","title":"Sao Man City ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sao-man-city-tien-cu-tai-nang-tre-thay-the-de-bruyne.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 bi quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Phil Foden v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0n anh h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-nhan-tin-cuc-soc-ve-de-bruyne-172-194571.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c</span> ngay \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi Kevin De Bruyne d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t s\u00e2n Etihad n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nghi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 2-3 th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phil Foden thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phil Foden thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/sao-man-city-tien-cu-tai-nang-tre-thay-the-de-bruyne.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Phil Foden thay th\u1ebf De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho Man City?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111i t\u1eeb bi quan \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n khi chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Kyle Walker tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Phil Foden c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Man City.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Phil Foden s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh: \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Kevin l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 Phil, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe, h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cT\u00f4i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Phil, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 17. Kh\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ti\u1ec7c t\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Huddersfield Town. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Arsenal ngay t\u1ea1i Emirates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-bi-nguoi-cu-mikel-arteta-phan-boi-nhu-the-nao-172-194558.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/arsenal-da-bi-nguoi-cu-mikel-arteta-phan-boi-nhu-the-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-bi-nguoi-cu-mikel-arteta-phan-boi-nhu-the-nao-172-194558.html\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Mikel Arteta \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i\u201d nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Pep Guardiola, ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man City \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2463","checkdouble":"194652"},{"date":"11:01 17/08","title":"Emery gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i Arsenal nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/emery-giai-quyet-con-khung-hoang-canh-trai-arsenal-nhu-the-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2n binh Stephan Lichtsteiner \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o sang b\u00ean kia \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n khi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Arsenal kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">N\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n g\u1ea5p b\u1ed9i cho Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, khi Ainsley Maitland-Niles s\u1edbm d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf Emirates, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng 20 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb trong v\u00f2ng hai th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o v\u00ec kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o v\u00ec kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/emery-giai-quyet-con-khung-hoang-canh-trai-arsenal-nhu-the-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lichtsteiner c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Hung tin n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Maitland-Niles, c\u1ea3 Sead Kolasinac v\u00e0 Nacho Monreal c\u0169ng ng\u1ed3i ch\u01a1i x\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean ch\u00ednh cho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">D\u00f9 sao, Unai Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, khi Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay th\u1ebf Maitland-Niles tr\u00e1m \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n em. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u00e2n binh k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u1ed1n s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cCh\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t. Maitland-Niles th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Lichtsteiner c\u0169ng v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Monreal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u r\u1ed3i.\u201d - Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2462","checkdouble":"194653"},{"date":"09:19 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Myanmar vs U23 Saudi Arabia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url