tion-color: initial;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Albacete vs Deportivo: 0-0</h2>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Albacete ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 17 chung cu\u1ed9c trong s\u1ed1 22 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Segunda (gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2 T\u00e2y Ban Nha), nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn b\u1edfi h\u1ecd ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb h\u1ea1ng 3. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Albacete r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan (th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 1 v\u00e0 thua 1)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Deportivo ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. So v\u1edbi th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 21 Deportivo gi\u1edd qu\u00e1 suy t\u00e0n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTuy v\u1eady, gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2 xem ra l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Riazor. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Krohn-Dehli, Carles Gil hay \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Pedro Mosquera... \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19, Deportivo l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Albacete. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1 xa c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br />\r\n+ Hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Deportivo v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2455","checkdouble":"194660"},{"date":"10:20 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Schweinfurt vs Schalke 01h45 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-schweinfurt-vs-schalke-01h45-ngay-188-cup-quoc-gia-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Schweinfurt vs Schalke l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Schweinfurt vs Schalke 01h45 ng\u00e0y 188 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Schweinfurt vs Schalke 01h45 ng\u00e0y 188 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/Schweinfurt-vs-Schalke.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Schweinfurt vs Schalke</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Schweinfurt vs Schalke: 1-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Schalke 04 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Bundesliga khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng Dortmund, Bayer Leverkusen hay RB Leipzig \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00c1 qu\u00e2n sau vua Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Schalke c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 thua \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Bundesliga v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh, n\u00ean \u201cHo\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebf xanh\u201d ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Schweinfurt - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p - \u1edf c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSchweinfurt ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 4 \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1ea3i qua 6 v\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 h\u00f2a. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho 1 su\u1ea5t th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng 3 m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.. D\u00f9 v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc Schalke 04, Scheweinfurt v\u1eabn qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSchweinfurt ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Schalke 04, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf b\u00e0n thua.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2454","checkdouble":"194661"},{"date":"07:20 17/08","title":"Emery \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Cech, x\u1eed ph\u0169 v\u1edbi Leno","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/emery-dat-niem-tin-vao-cech-xu-phu-voi-leno.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Petr Cech s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn derby London gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cech \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Nh\u01b0ng sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Petr Cech.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Bernd Leno v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 19.2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 Leverkusen, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Leno c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh. B\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Petr Cech kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Cech, x\u1eed ph\u0169 v\u1edbi Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emery \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Cech, x\u1eed ph\u0169 v\u1edbi Leno h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/emery-dat-niem-tin-vao-cech-xu-phu-voi-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV&nbsp;Emery \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Cech</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLeno c\u00f3 v\u1ebb h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Emery. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u HLV Paris Saint-Germain m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3m Cech \u1edf tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Petr Cech c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Leno xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Cech. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Bernd Leno. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c nhau. T\u00f9y theo c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nCech \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 11 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Chelsea, ra s\u00e2n 333 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League n\u0103m 2011/12. Ngo\u00e0i ra, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 4 danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal n\u0103m 2015, danh hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Cech c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u FA Cup \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-tu-sanh-minh-voi-ronaldo-va-salah-172-194565.html\">Sao Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-arsenal-tu-tin-soan-ngoi-vo-dich-cua-man-city-172-194563.html\">T\u00e2n binh Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2453","checkdouble":"194645"},{"date":"07:50 17/08","title":"Pochettino d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Spurs","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/pochettino-du-doan-ve-mot-mua-giai-kho-khan-o-spurs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Tottenham.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong top 3 Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1eabn l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t Spurs gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 \u1edf League Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf Premier League \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u00ec Tottenham ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Spurs c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Spurs h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Spurs h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/pochettino-du-doan-ve-mot-mua-giai-kho-khan-o-spurs.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Spurs</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho HLV Pochettino tin r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ebfn Tottenham n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;100% l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 200% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c. Trong t\u00e2m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n hay \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPochettino \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Tottenham v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 CLB chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;S\u1ebd th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec Tottenham mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i &lsquo;ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0o&rsquo;. B\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-se-chi-200-trieu-euro-mua-eriksen-neu-modric-ra-di-180-194557.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Eriksen n\u1ebfu Modric ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eric-dier-khong-co-tan-binh-tottenham-van-du-suc-vao-top-4-172-194409.html\">Eric Dier: Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u00e0o Top 4</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2452","checkdouble":"194646"},{"date":"07:27 17/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Bahrain vs U23 Kyrgyzstan 16h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-bahrain-vs-u23-kyrgyzstan-16h00-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Bahrain vs U23 Kyrgyzstan l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (V\u0